'''Langley Memorial Hospital''' is a government-funded [[acute care]] facility, and Level IV [[trauma centre]] in [[Township of Langley]], British Columbia that is owned and operated by [[Fraser Health]].

==Philanthropic affiliation==
* [http://www.lmhfoundation.com Memorial Hospital Foundation]
* [http://www.langleymemorialhospitalauxiliary.ca Memorial Hospital Auxiliary]

